title: China Gate 1957 | Action, war film | Lee Van Cleef & Nat King Cole | Directed by Samuel Fuller

sources.title: China Gate 1957 | Action, war film | Lee Van Cleef & Nat King Cole | Directed by Samuel Fuller
sources.description:
In 1954, during the French Indochina War, an Eurasian female smuggler and a group of French Foreign Legion mercenaries, infiltrate the enemy territory in order to destroy an arms depot.

Colorized version: https://youtu.be/suPQtLY4M3M


Original title: China Gate (1957) 
Alternative titles: Gates of China, La puerta de China, Las puertas rojas, Corredor hacia China, La porta della Cina, A Porta da China, Porte de Chine, China-Legionär, 关山劫, チャイナ・ゲイト, No Umbral da China, 차이나 게이트

Director & Writer: Samuel Fuller
Stars: Gene Barry, Angie Dickinson, Nat 'King' Cole, & Lee Van Cleef
Genres: Action, Drama, War

This film has Spanish audio, and subtitled in many languages.
